{"tid":1048390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國正式公告 美中貿易「停戰期」無定期延長","createTime":"2019-03-05T15:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T13:36:17.000Z","uid":35790,"like":13,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"03a59f01b711eccd4feba0ec5b3fb7504f9c2589","tid":1048390,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"美國正式公告 美中貿易「停戰期」無定期延長<br />\n<br />\n美國政府5日正式確認，將美中貿易「停戰期」無定期延長；「直到進一步通告」之前，美國對2,000億美元中國產品所加徵的10%懲罰性關稅稅率不會提高，也不會擴大加徵關稅的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表署在「聯邦公報」中發表聲明指出，「2018年9月調查行動所涵蓋中國產品新增關稅稅率提高到25%的實施日期予以延後」。<br />\n&lt;聯合&gt;"},{"pid":"4341ae09451987ed2732ffacbb5d5c32a0c3dd15","tid":1048390,"uid":42921,"like":115,"dislike":3,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:25:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69360e52974174c288114aa0f1df83511614955","tid":1048390,"uid":155095,"like":17,"dislike":7,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"貿易戰～完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7275ad9548640b0bb54460e8685533bd49fc1fdb","tid":1048390,"uid":174530,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:45:24.000Z","msg":"中國已死"},{"pid":"bd76bfac23a8174549150789edf6cef014414f6e","tid":1048390,"uid":82929,"like":88,"dislike":2,"score":86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又縮<br />\n即係美國都奈支那唔何啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街啦，世界真係準備全面倒退都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望1984唔好發生<img src